{"tid":1459620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講左咁耐 都話要攻擊冇gear既狗！！","createTime":"2019-08-12T18:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T20:58:04.000Z","uid":238171,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cf2e04169e8f0924d35a6884f51b7dbe8b462076","tid":1459620,"uid":238171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:34:31.000Z","msg":"貼左幾日連儂牆發現左針對人格既文宣係極快比人撕走！！ 證明左針對人格式既文宣係超級重要！！<br />\n<br />\n明白有勇氣用麻包袋既人少之有少 但除左物攻仲有精神攻擊！ 好多巴打都提過塞爾維亞人既案例 同大家重溫一下：<br />\n<br />\n[案例討論] 塞爾維亞人教你，咩叫禍不及妻兒，請各位參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1448757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1448757</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少呢啲精神壓力 其實狗仔係因為著左gear 冇人認得出先會咁撚「英勇」試諗諗狗仔離開左狗群 冇左gear 就只係一隻過街老鼠 本身體力已經耗盡再加埋呢啲壓力 後果不言而喻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我希望有多啲<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">針對式</span></strong>既文宣出現 唔止係貼濫用暴力既圖 仲要加止<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人格抵毀</span></strong></span>既字眼！！<br />\n<br />\n例如呢類整既文宣圖：<br />\n<br />\n不如print 出來貼警察宿舍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我地做既係要不斷放大同提醒一直而來既社會規範 eg: 父母要保護子女 警察係代表正義......<br />\n再貼上不同既圖證明佢地先係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暴徙、rule breakers!!</span></span> 冇野慘得過全部人孤立你個種空虛感！<br />\n<br />\n講左咁多野其實係小妹同朋友整左啲文宣圖比大家<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S6DuQa7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS6DuQa7.png&h=fa0330b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j3dR3v9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj3dR3v9.png&h=5d039035&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yP0kWRa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyP0kWRa.png&h=1961b42e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W3UBvbb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW3UBvbb.png&h=e1a62a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有啲英文版：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NJYVLKR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJYVLKR.jpg&h=a6d51891&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WBUegRy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWBUegRy.jpg&h=93721a41&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOXoabz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOXoabz.jpg&h=19d2a0cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5WbkcpW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5WbkcpW.jpg&h=2c3ecaba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地第一次整 冇經驗 好多細節未必做得好勿見怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔止警察宿舍 其實有好多私人屋宛早期都會批左一/兩座出去做狗舍 要貼到全香港每一個角落 要佢地永不超生！！ </span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8f68a9c1240887f4a9db9147f1a2849db423de0e","tid":1459620,"uid":238171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:34:46.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"af31574a76c183dedb2829dda860ce54092a35f9","tid":1459620,"uid":238171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:35:02.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"078b8baf8bf40189ef55ebbfaea454ddb1a41839","tid":1459620,"uid":238171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:35:19.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"844fbc1bdb7e31a5ae55568553a541b8866d5ed8","tid":1459620,"uid":238171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:35:33.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"058eddd9259555b28e75adfeab6fb9b190b57f1b","tid":1459620,"uid":238171,"like":0,"dislike"